Package io.github.clivelewis.cvrclient.model

Interface CvrCompanyDataModel

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CvrCompanyOnlyCvrNumber, CvrFullCompanyInfo, CvrMainCompanyInfo
    public interface CvrCompanyDataModel
    Marker interface for all CVR data model classes.
    Required by some methods in CvrClient.
    Sets the root element name for Jackson deserialization.
    Sets the 'Vrvirksomhed' prefix for all CvrField annotations in implementing classes.
